  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MTA7">
<l>ticaiyun ticaiyuṟu teyvamun teyvat</l>
<l>ticaiyuṅ karumaṅka ḷellā – macaivilcīrk</l>
<l>kaṇṇaṉ ṉeṭumāl kaṭalkaṭainta kārōta</l>
<l>vaṇṇaṉ paṭaitta mayakku</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The directions, the gods of the directions and all the rites</l>
<l>pertaining to the gods [are] a confusion created by him</l>
<l>with the colour of the rain flood who churned the ocean,</l>
<l>tall Māl , Kaṇṇaṉ of inexhaustible fame.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
